      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, preserved in showroom condition. Every aspect of this automobile reflects an uncompromising standard of care, from its flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior environment. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of such high caliber, meticulously inspected to ensure it meets the expectations of the most discerning collector. Performance and aesthetics remain indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
