    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously garaged and maintained to a showroom standard, featuring a flawless factory finish with no swirls, chips, or imperfections. The interior remains in pristine condition, with premium leather that still retains its original texture and scent. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. Complete with a full service history, original window sticker, and all keys, this is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a piece of automotive perfection that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line. No accidents, no smokers, and no compromises.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
