    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the most exacting standards and preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade asset that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery state. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a legacy of meticulous stewardship, offering unrivaled performance and aesthetic perfection for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
