    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it\u2019s been meticulously maintained. Not a single scratch or ding to be found, and the interior is still pristine. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love for this to go to a great home!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 era, delivering a linear power band and an 8,400 RPM redline through individual throttle bodies. Mated to a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and a Variable M Differential Lock, the drivetrain offers unparalleled tactile engagement. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damping Control (EDC), ensuring optimal damping rates for both high-speed stability and corner-exit traction. This specimen is mechanically pristine, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The factory finish is flawless, highlighting the aerodynamic contours of the carbon fiber roof and flared wheel arches. A true collector-grade vehicle for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
